{@--2@} As a prefix to nouns not
directly derived from verbs it means
({%a%}) likeness, resemblance, equality;
({%b%}) opposite, of the opposite side;
{#pratibala#} <ls>Ve. 3. 5</ls> ‘the opposing
force’; so {#pratidvipAH#} <ls>Mu. 2. 13</ls>; ({%c%})
rivalry; as in {#praticaMdraH#} ‘a rival moon’;
{#pratipuruzaH#} &c.

{@--3@} As a separable 
preposition (with <ab>acc.</ab>) it means ({%a%}) 

towards, in the direction of, to; {#tO#}
{#daMpatI svAM prati rAjaDAnIM prasTApayAmAsa#}
{#vaSI vasizWaH#} <ls>R. 2. 70</ls>; <ls n="R.">1. 75</ls>; {#pratyanilaM#}
{#viceruH#} <ls>Ku. 3. 31</ls>; {#vfkzaM prati vidyotate#}
{#vidyut#} <ls>Sk.</ls>; ({%b%}) against, counter, in
opposition to, opposite; {#tadA#} 
{#yAyAdripuM prati#} <ls>Ms. 7. 171</ls>; {#pradudruvustaM prati#} 
{#rAkzaseMdraM#} <ls>Rām.</ls>; {#yayAvajaH pratyarisEnyameva#}  
<ls>R. 7. 55</ls>; ({%c%}) in comparison with, on a
par with, in proportion to, a match
for; {#tvaM sahasrARi prati#} <ls>Rv. 2. 1. 8</ls>; ({%d%})
near, in the vicinity of, by, at, in,
on; {#samAsedustato gaMgAM SfMgaverapuraM prati#}
<ls>Rām.</ls>; {#gaMgAM prati#}; ({%e%}) at the time,
about, during; {#AdityasyodayaM prati#} <ls>Mb.</ls>;
{#PAlgunaM vATa cEtraM vA mAsO prati#}  
<ls>Ms. 7. 182</ls>; ({%f%}) on the side of, in favour
of, to the lot of; {#yadatra mAM prati syAt#}
<ls>Sk.</ls>; {#haraM prati halAhalaM (aBavat)#} <ls>Vop.</ls>;
({%g%}) in each, in or at every, 
severally (used in a distributive sense);
{#varzaM prati, prativarzaM; yajYaM prati#} <ls>Y. 1. 110</ls>;
{#vfkzaM vfkzaM prati siMcati#} <ls>Sk.</ls>; ({%h%}) with
regard or reference to, in 
relation to, regarding, 
concerning, about, as to; {#na hi me#} 
{#saMSItirasyA divyatAM prati#} <ls>K. 132</ls>; {#caMdroparAgaM#}
{#prati tu kenApi vipralabDAsi#} <ls>Mu. 1</ls>; {#DarmaM#}
