<ls>Y. 1. 218</ls>; <ls>R. 6. 12</ls>; <ls n="R.">10. 29</ls>; <ls n="R.">12. 51</ls>;
({%i%}) according to, in conformity
with; {#mAM prati#} in my opinion; ({%j%})
before, in the presence of; ({%k%}) for,
on account of.

